channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: The World Will Be Swimming in Excess Oil by End of This Decade, IEA Says
item.description: The global energy watchdog has forecast a major glut, citing surging supplies and slowing demand growth thanks to lower-emission energy sources.
